  "conformsTo": "http://mlcommons.org/croissant/1.1",
  "name": "clinical-trial-decision-benchmark",
  "description": "\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\tNo-Human Clinical-Trial Decision Benchmark (v1)\n\t\n\nEach record is a completed clinical trial with a decision label: advance, stop, verify, or abstain.\nThe labels are derived automatically from public evidence, with no human curation. The task is to decide\nwhether a program should advance, stop, or be deferred on the evidence available, and to abstain when the\nevidence is too thin to call. The dataset includes construct-validity checks and a temporal train/test\nsplit so that scores… See the full description on the dataset page: https://huggingface.co/datasets/jang1563/clinical-trial-decision-benchmark.",
